{"tid":2024561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文就職演說將重申絕不接受一國兩制","createTime":"2020-05-19T16:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T16:41:07.000Z","uid":9031,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63b663074fa766a1b3819a6a283929453645adac","tid":2024561,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】在台灣，蔡英文將會展開第二個總統任期，她會在就職演說中重申絕不接受一國兩制，未來目標是維持台海和平穩定。她接受台灣傳媒專訪提到，對台灣未來充滿信心。<br />\n<br />\n總統府表示，蔡英文周三發表的就職演說將提到兩岸互動，重申和平、對等、民主、對話的基本原則，絕不接受一國兩制、矮化台灣、破壞現狀的做法，未來兩岸事務亦會根據憲法處理，目標是維持台海和平穩定。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧發聲明，恭賀蔡英文連任總統，指今次疫情令國際社會有機會看到台灣防疫模式是值得效法，美國長期將台灣視為值得依賴的夥伴，相信在蔡英文的帶領下，雙方關係將持續蓬勃發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=391572&amp;fbclid=IwAR2W2F6TSChRXzRdjlbPYE-7Stv8jsJ-qMVkMLlicFIXd2GswlDTN8cgiok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391572%26fbclid%3DIwAR2W2F6TSChRXzRdjlbPYE-7Stv8jsJ-qMVkMLlicFIXd2GswlDTN8cgiok&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7mo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=0a6b99dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391572%26fbclid%3DIwAR2W2F6TSChRXzRdjlbPYE-7Stv8jsJ-qMVkMLlicFIXd2GswlDTN8cgiok&h=0db61eef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=391572&amp;fbclid=IwAR2W2F6TSChRXzRdjlbPYE-7Stv8jsJ-qMVkMLlicFIXd2GswlDTN8cgiok</a>"},{"pid":"84f9fb504b6adc11921b333062197c92fe4b0455","tid":2024561,"uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MFQYpb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMFQYpb5.jpg&h=5349f965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問心 大家想唔想香港獨立建國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024303</a>"},{"pid":"0850edf6692847ce117e6dce4f80b1038d77178f","tid":2024561,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s